verses.roman:
jaya jaya śrī-kṛṣṇa-caitanya gauracandra
jaya jayādvaita jaya jaya nityānanda

synonyms: jaya jaya—all glories; śrī-kṛṣṇa-caitanya—to Lord Śrī Caitanya Mahāprabhu; gauracandra—whose name is Gaurahari; jaya jaya—all glories; advaita—to Advaita Gosāñi; jaya jaya—all glories; nityānanda—to Nityānanda.
translation: All glories to Śrī Kṛṣṇa Caitanya, who is known as Gaurahari! All glories to Advaita and Nityānanda Prabhu!
